"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-01--Made-in-China-shines-at-the-Paris-Olympics-1vIccsMRfd6-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  T-House  Copied  Did you know these products are made in China? The Paris 2024 Organising Committee reveals that 80 percent of the mascots are produced by Chinese manufacturers. Plus, Chinese technology is making a significant impact throughout the Games. Experience how China-made tech is set to enhance the Olympics with stunning visuals and cutting-edge innovation!  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"